{"id":144744,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/原公安厅长揭秘：三年大饥荒为何没有出现大规模/","date":"2011-04-15T07:00:45Z","modified":"2011-04-15T07:00:45Z","title":"原公安厅长揭秘：三年大饥荒为何没有出现大规模动乱","content":"<p>“大跃进”以后，全国大饥荒，饿死了几千万人。饿死这么多人，为什么没有出现大规模的动乱？这是因为，国家采取了严密而严厉的社会控制措施。用镇压反革命运动的手段推动政治运动的&#8230;<img src=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/t1/499761087/hihistory/feedsky/s.gif?r=http://hihistory.net/post/10881/\" border=\"0\" height=\"0\" width=\"0\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/r/l/feedsky/hihistory/499761087/art01.html\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/r/i/feedsky/hihistory/499761087/art01.gif\"></a></p>\n</p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=752465\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"Subscribe me!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[20534],"tags":[]}